alspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/170554-betelgeuse/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Betelgeuse\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s showtime...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Urses","CreatedById":175990,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-02T00:05:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223006289\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022158535\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221491090291\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289014\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022adsii1970\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 minutes ago, adsii1970 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s showtime...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWas it not\u00A0more?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n@Beetlejuice\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n@Beetlejuice\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n@... nahnah 3times is a bad choice\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/176397-ed-jaws/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022176397\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/176397-ed-jaws/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Ed Jaws\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWelcome in the Chaos and have a nice Stay /wink\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPS: and you are only so old how you Feel you... Hmmm this means i am sometimes 220\u002B ... (\u00D75\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:wink:\u0022\u003E) Sorry i am not english native.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ed Jaws","CreatedById":176397,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-03T13:25:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA short update, I bought KSP from the Squad store over the weekend. Contrary to the demo download the full game downloaded super fast, probably less then a minute.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDefinitely happy I bought it from the devs direct. I could care less about tracking my playing time as using Steam would give me. All that gives is bragging rights which doesn\u0027t interest me.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTo me, learning a game is just as much fun as completing it. The short time I\u0027ve played I\u0027ve managed to kill Jeb numerous times, poor guy. The funniest one is when the rocket didn\u0027t even lift off. It just tipped over and exploded, silly me.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you all for helping a newcomer.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPS. Thanks for the tip \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/123837-dman979/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022123837\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/123837-dman979/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Dman979\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:wink:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}